snippet: Officials have spoken openly, if vaguely, of using cyberstrikes and exotic forms of sabotage to redefine antimissile defense for the United States....

headline.main: Trump Inherits a Secret Cyberwar Against North Korean Missiles
headline.print_headline: Trump Inherits Secret Cyberwar on North Korea

lead_paragraph: Officials have spoken openly, if vaguely, of using cyberstrikes and exotic forms of sabotage to redefine antimissile defense for the United States.
